WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:02.910
Agentation helps a logged-in TYPO3

2
00:00:02.930 --> 00:00:04.960
user report a precise interface

3
00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:06.985
issue to a coding agent.

4
00:00:07.005 --> 00:00:08.090
The user points to an

5
00:00:08.110 --> 00:00:09.740
element, adds a note, and

6
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:12.010
sends useful page details with

7
00:00:12.030 --> 00:00:14.225
it. When enabled, TYPO3 passes

8
00:00:14.245 --> 00:00:15.770
the request through its own

9
00:00:15.790 --> 00:00:17.110
server so the server key

10
00:00:17.130 --> 00:00:19.065
stays out of the browser.

11
00:00:19.085 --> 00:00:20.905
The video shows setup only;

12
00:00:20.925 --> 00:00:22.785
no live sync completes.

13
00:00:22.805 --> 00:00:24.640
The feature page explains setup,

14
00:00:24.660 --> 00:00:26.640
access limits, and the hand-off.
